Package com.github.dylon.liblevenshtein.levenshtein.distance

Various implementations of Levenshtein distance.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDistance<Term>
    Specifies the interface that all distance functions must implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMemoized
    Common, initialization logic for memoized, distance metrics.
    MemoizedMergeAndSplit
    Memoizes the distance between two terms, where the distance is calculated using the standard Levenshtein distance extended with merge and split.
    MemoizedStandard
    Memoizes the distance between two terms, where the distance is calculated using the standard Levenshtein distance, including the elementary operations of insertion, deletion and substitution.
    MemoizedTransposition
    Memoizes the distance between two terms, where the distance is calculated using the standard Levenshtein distance extended with transposition.
